    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/domain-context-to-application-routing/000",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "microbeMASST is a community-sourced tool that works within the GNPS ecosystem. Users can search tandem MS (MS/MS) spectra obtained from their experiments against the GNPS/MassIVE repository",
      "asbval:note": "Paper describes microbeMASST as a single domain-specific tool for microbial metabolomics. No evidence of a conditional routing mechanism that dispatches to multiple domain-specific MASST variants (plantMASST, tissueMASST, microbiomeMASST, foodMASST, metadataMASST). The paper focuses exclusively on microbeMASST; other MASST variants are not mentioned or discussed.",
