      "asbval:note": "Paper confirms batch processing Python script for microbeMASST only. No evidence that jobs.py orchestrates searches across multiple domain-specific MASST tools (plantMASST, tissueMASST, etc.). The script is confirmed for microbeMASST batch searches, not cross-domain aggregation.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10-1038-s41564-023-01575-9",
