      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "microbeMASST is a community-sourced tool that works within the GNPS ecosystem. Users can search tandem MS (MS/MS) spectra obtained from their experiments against the GNPS/MassIVE repository",
      "asbval:note": "Paper describes microbeMASST as a single domain-specific MASST application for microbial spectra. No evidence of routing logic to multiple domain-specific MASST variants (plantMASST, tissueMASST, microbiomeMASST, foodMASST, metadataMASST). The card claims a routing/dispatch system across six domain-specific applications; the paper only documents microbeMASST itself.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10-1038-s41564-023-01575-9",
      "asbval:supported_raw": "partial",
      "asbval:target_artifact_id": "web-application-endpoint-mapping",
      "asbval:target_artifact_kind": "skill_bundle",
      "asbval:target_claim_field": "research_question",
      "asbval:target_claim_text": "Route user-submitted mass spectrometry spectra to domain-specific MASST web applications based on parsed domain context (microbial, plant, tissue, microbiome, food, or metadata aggregation)",
      "eco:evidence_type": {
        "@id": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000361"
      },
      "prov:wasAttributedTo": "anthropic/claude-haiku-4-5-20251001",
      "prov:wasGeneratedAtTime": "2026-06-15T21:24:10.727339+00:00",
      "sepio:credibility_status": {
        "@id": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/SEPIO_0000339"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/web-application-endpoint-mapping/001",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "microbeMASST is a community-sourced tool that works within the GNPS ecosystem. Different from MASST, which uses a precomputed network of ~110 million MS/MS spectra to enable spectral searching, microbeMASST is based on the recently introduced Fast Search Tool",
      "asbval:note": "Paper confirms GNPS ecosystem and MASST framework exist, but only documents microbeMASST as one instantiation. No evidence of six domain-specific variants or a unified routing framework across them. The card's claim of GNPS_MASST providing framework for 'all six domain-specific MASST standalone applications' is not supported; paper only describes microbeMASST.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10-1038-s41564-023-01575-9",
      "asbval:supported_raw": "partial",
      "asbval:target_artifact_id": "web-application-endpoint-mapping",
      "asbval:target_artifact_kind": "skill_bundle",
      "asbval:target_claim_field": "tools",
      "asbval:target_claim_text": "GNPS_MASST: Provides the underlying code and web application framework for all six domain-specific MASST standalone applications",
      "eco:evidence_type": {
        "@id": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000361"
      },
      "prov:wasAttributedTo": "anthropic/claude-haiku-4-5-20251001",
      "prov:wasGeneratedAtTime": "2026-06-15T21:24:10.727339+00:00",
      "sepio:credibility_status": {
        "@id": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/SEPIO_0000339"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/web-application-endpoint-mapping/002",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "microbeMASST, a taxonomically informed mass spectrometry (MS) search tool, tackles limited microbial metabolite annotation in untargeted metabolomics experiments. Leveraging a curated database of >60,000 microbial monocultures, users can search known and unknown MS/MS spectra and link them to their respective microbial producers via MS/MS fragmentation patterns.",
      "asbval:note": "Confirmed: microbeMASST is designed for microbial spectra and searches against a curated microbial database.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10-1038-s41564-023-01575-9",
      "asbval:supported_raw": "yes",
      "asbval:target_artifact_id": "web-application-endpoint-mapping",
      "asbval:target_artifact_kind": "skill_bundle",
      "asbval:target_claim_field": "tools",
      "asbval:target_claim_text": "microbeMASST: Target endpoint for spectra with microbial domain context; searches against microbial metabolite spectral library",
      "eco:evidence_type": {
        "@id": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000033"
      },
      "prov:wasAttributedTo": "anthropic/claude-haiku-4-5-20251001",
